# Wallet Connectors

Xellar-Kit provides several wallet connection options:

## Supported Wallets

- **Xellar Passport**: Main wallet integration in [src/xellar-connector/](mdc:packages/xellar-kit/src/xellar-connector)
- **MetaMask (Injected)**: Support for injected web3 wallets
- **WalletConnect**: QR code-based connection

## Key Components

- [packages/xellar-kit/src/wallets/](mdc:packages/xellar-kit/src/wallets) - Contains wallet implementations
- [packages/xellar-kit/src/components/dialog/content/connect-dialog.tsx](mdc:packages/xellar-kit/src/components/dialog/content/connect-dialog.tsx) - Main connection dialog
- [packages/xellar-kit/src/hooks/use-xellar-account.ts](mdc:packages/xellar-kit/src/hooks/use-xellar-account.ts) - Hook for accessing Xellar account data

## Configuration

The wallet connection can be configured using the `defaultConfig` function exported from [packages/xellar-kit/src/config/default-config.ts](mdc:packages/xellar-kit/src/config/default-config.ts)
